{"tid":2224569,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"記協明日派義務觀察員記錄警方對傳媒作出的安排","createTime":"2020-09-30T15:04:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T16:45:57.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"155098f9b5a391dc620a5058e40b323f1169ceca","tid":2224569,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T15:04:28.000Z","msg":"記協表示，明天國慶日及中秋節假期，預計有市民響應網民號召上街，將會是警方修改《警察通例》中「傳媒代表」定義後，首個大型公眾活動，記協將試行「觀察員計劃」，安排3名義務觀察員，包括記協執委、新聞系講師及現職新聞從業員，到港島區公眾活動現場進行記錄。<br />\n<br />\n3名觀察員將穿着螢光綠色背心，貼上「觀察員Observer」的標籤。他們將以中立身分在公眾活動現場，記錄警方對傳媒作出的安排、警隊傳媒聯絡隊工作時的行為表現，以及現場記者的行為表現等。<br />\n<br />\n觀察員可能利用拍攝器材錄影或訪談，以記錄發生的相關事項，有關材料將用於但不限於記協內部研究或法律訴訟，材料的閱覽權只限記協執委會或經執委會授權的相關人士。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1552536-20200930.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1552536-20200930.htm&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kypFDRn80AWZfiUxX1c6OkmY%3D&h=6454451b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1552536-20200930.htm&h=ed80a7c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1552536-20200930.htm</a>"},{"pid":"5575ad4df964802d5e35330cae7d2c52f357b2b3","tid":2224569,"uid":11291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T15:07:10.000Z","msg":"聽日班黑警實鳩拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac15335ea8aba232c610df0a7033bd07d7a5f656","tid":2224569,"uid":6058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T15:10:35.000Z","msg":"拉撚埋你班觀察員就有<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d24e9d1584e0042ef838ab8d19da3dd7f6cd7a18","tid":2224569,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T15:12:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2